videos.description: Kris Wilkes creates some space and knocks down a 3-pointer for the Bruins.
videos.headline: Wilkes buries triple for UCLA

videos.description: Aaron Holiday pulls up in transition and knocks down the 3-pointer in traffic.
videos.headline: Holiday knocks down no-hesitation triple

videos.description: Daejon Davis is left open and makes UCLA pay by knocking down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Davis drains 3-pointer to cut into UCLA lead

videos.description: Stanford's Oscar da Silva knocks down a 3-pointer as the product of good ball movement.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to da Silva corner triple

videos.description: Thomas Welsh banks in a 15-foot jumper for the Bruins.
videos.headline: Welsh calls bank for UCLA

videos.description: Prince Ali splits defenders and finds an open Alex Olesinski for the corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Ali drives and kicks to an open Olesinski for the triple

videos.description: UCLA's Gyorgy Goloman sees an open lane and rips through for the dunk.
videos.headline: Goloman clears the lane for slam
